Package: regnans
Title: Package for assembling communities with the plant model
Version: 0.2
Author: Daniel S. Falster and Richard G. FitzJohn
Maintainer: Daniel S. Falster <daniel.falster@unsw.edu.au>
Description: Assembles ecological communities of competing strategies using the
    plant model, by iterating demography to equilibrium, computing selection
    gradients and invasion fitness, and solving for evolutionary attractors.
License: BSD_2_clause + file LICENSE
Depends:
    R (>= 4.5.0)
Imports:
    plant,
    Rcpp,
    lhs,
    mvtnorm,
    dfoptim,
    ggplot2,
    BB,
    nleqslv,
    purrr,
    dplyr,
    tidyr,
    tibble,
    mlr3,
    mlr3learners,
    mlr3mbo,
    bbotk,
    paradox,
    data.table,
    logger,
    crayon
LinkingTo:
    Rcpp
Remotes:
    traitecoevo/plant
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    parallel
Encoding: UTF-8
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Config/testthat/parallel: true
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
